NK106(me)009:1: // rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso'i bsdus don
NK106(me)009:2: man+d+aa ra ba'i phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so
NK106(me)009:3: // dpal kun du bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)009:4: 'dir rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso'i don rgya cher dbye ba la gsum ste /
NK106(me)009:7: bstan bcos yongs su rdzogs pa'i bya ba'o //
NK106(me)009:9: skad gnyis shan sbyar ba mtshan gyi don /
NK106(me)009:10: mdo dang rgyas pas phyag gi don /
NK106(me)009:12: gnyis pa la le'u brgyad las /
NK106(me)009:13: chos thams cad rmi lam lta bu bstan pa'i le'u dang po la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:14: chos thams cad rmi lam du gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK106(me)009:15: ji ltar nyams su blang ba'i rim pa'o //
NK106(me)009:17: dbyings la sems can gyi 'khrul tshul dang /
NK106(me)009:18: 'khrul dus ji ltar gnas tshul bsten pa'o //
NK106(me)009:20: gdod ma gzhi'i gnas tshul lhan cig skyes pa dang /
NK106(me)009:21: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas 'khrul pa glo bur du snang tshul /
NK106(me)009:22: bag chags brtas pa las so sor snang ba dang /
NK106(me)009:23: gcig las du mar snang bas 'khrul snang 'khor ba'i grub tshul bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:25: 'khrul snang log rtog sgyu mar bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:26: de nyid bden med rdzun snang du bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:27: snang yang gzhi med rtsa bral du bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:28: med snang stong pa'i rang gzugs su bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:29: gnas lugs chos nyid rnam dag tu bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:30: gnyis pa ji ltar nyams su blang ba'i rim pa bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)009:32: sgom pas nyams su blang ba /
NK106(me)009:35: sngon 'gro dang dngos gzhi bsgom tshul lo //
NK106(me)009:39: chos nyid stong pa'i rdzogs rim mo //
NK106(me)009:41: nyin mo rnal 'byor gyi rim pa dang /
NK106(me)009:42: mtshan mo rnal 'byor gyi bsgom tshul lo //
NK106(me)009:46: gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa'i rtsa ba bcad pa'o //
NK106(me)009:49: nang yul can rmi lam du blta bas don rang
NK106(me)009:50: mtshan du zhen pa lhan skyes nyon sgrib kyi sgrib
NK106(me)009:51: pa sbyang ba / 'das da lta ma 'ongs pa'i
NK106(me)009:52: chos su gtogs pa rmi lam du blta bas don
NK106(me)009:53: spyi mtshan du zhen pa kun brtags shes sgrib kyi
NK106(me)009:55: byung tshor rmi lam du blta bas 'khrul rtsa bdag 'dzin gyi dri ma sbyong ba'o //
NK106(me)009:56: gnyis pa ldang ba'i rnal 'byor la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:58: snang ba'i bya byed rmi lam du shes pas lam khyer dang po dang /
NK106(me)009:59: de'i man ngag bden med du rtsa la sbyong ba'o //
NK106(me)009:60: gsum pa 'khrul pa'i rtsa ba bcad pa la drug ste /
NK106(me)009:61: gzung yul gzhi med rtsa bral du bstan pas gzung rtog gi rtsa ba bcad pa /
NK106(me)009:62: 'dzin pa rtsa bral du bstan pas 'dzin rtog gi rtsa ba bcad pa /
NK106(me)009:63: yul sems rten med du rtogs pas gdod ma'i gzhi la bskyal ba /
NK106(me)009:64: de nyid don la goms pas 'khrul snang dbyings su dag pa /
NK106(me)009:65: med snang stong pa'i rang gzugs bag chags rmi lam du bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:66: 'thad pa dpe yis dgod pas gzhi med rtsa bral du bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:67: gnyis pa mtshan mo rnal 'byor gyi bsgom tshul la bdun te /
NK106(me)009:68: gnad las rmi lam bsgom pa /
NK106(me)009:74: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa bsgrub pa'o //
NK106(me)009:75: gsum pa 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:76: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu'o //
NK106(me)009:77: de nas chos thams cad sgyu ma lta bur bstan pa'i le'u gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:78: le'u rtsom pa la 'jug pa'i tshul dang /
NK106(me)009:81: chos thams cad sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du shes par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)009:82: shes nas ji ltar nyams su blang ba'i rim pa'o //
NK106(me)009:84: gdod ma'i dbyings las 'khor ba'i 'khrul tshul spyir bstan /
NK106(me)009:85: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du gtan la 'bebs tshul bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK106(me)009:86: sgyu ma rigs gsum du chos rnams 'dus tshul gyi don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)009:88: sems nyid gdod ma'i gnas lugs /
NK106(me)009:90: gzung 'dzin bag chags kyi dbang gis 'khor ba sna
NK106(me)009:91: tshogs su 'khor bas 'khrul dus bden med kyi snang
NK106(me)009:92: lugs so // gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)009:93: sgyu ma'i gnas lugs stong nyid mdor bstan /
NK106(me)009:94: sgyu ma'i snang tshul rim gyis rgyas par bshad /
NK106(me)009:95: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin rten 'brel du don bsdu ba'o //
NK106(me)009:97: sgyu ma rigs bzhi'i go don spyir bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:98: so so'i rang bzhin bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)009:100: rnam dbye dngos de dag dpe'i sgyu ma'i gtan la 'bebs tshul /
NK106(me)009:101: dpe don shan sbyar bas sgyu ma rigs bzhi'i go don sbyar ba'o //
NK106(me)009:104: ngo bo phyogs lhung gnyis med /
NK106(me)009:106: 'char tshul dpe don nges 'byed kyi rang bzhin sgyu ma /
NK106(me)009:109: dpe'i sgyu ma'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)009:110: gsum pa sgyu ma rten 'brel du bsdu ba la drug ste /
NK106(me)009:112: ngo bo stong nyid kyi rang bzhin /
NK106(me)009:113: rnam pa sgyu ma'i dpe don /
NK106(me)009:115: sgyu ma rang snang gi snying rje /
NK106(me)009:116: gshis don chos nyid kyi dbyings rum du bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:117: gsum pa rigs gsum du don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:118: chos rnams sgyu mar gdams pa dang /
NK106(me)009:119: shes byed 'thad pa dgod pas sgyu ma'i tshul la spyir gdams pa dang /
NK106(me)009:123: sgyu ma rigs gsum gyi gnas bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)009:124: don gnyis pa shes nas ji ltar nyams su blang ba'i rim pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)009:127: sgom pa de dag pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK106(me)009:131: gzung 'dzin gzhig pa dang gsum gyis nyin mo rnal 'byor du bya ba dang /
NK106(me)009:133: rmi lam sbyong bas mtshan mo rnal 'byor du bya'o //
NK106(me)009:134: de nas chos thams cad mig yor lta bur bstan pa'i le'u gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:138: chos thams cad mig yor gyi tshul du shes par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)009:139: de nas ji ltar nyams su blang ba'i rim pa'o //
NK106(me)009:141: dbyings las 'khrul snang gi shar tshul bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)009:142: stong pa rang snang gi rol par bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:144: 'od gsal snying po'i rang ngo ma shes pas 'khrul pa dang /
NK106(me)009:145: med snang stong pa la bdag tu gzung bas 'khrul par bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:149: dpe don nges pa'i chos nyid /
NK106(me)009:150: med pa gzung ba'i snang tshul /
NK106(me)009:151: snang la 'dzin med kyi gdams tshul /
NK106(me)009:152: mi rtog mnyam pa'i dgongs don /
NK106(me)009:153: rgya grol 'dzin med kyi rang gnad /
NK106(me)009:154: bden med stong pa'i thag chod bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:155: gnyis pa shes nas nyams su blang ba'i rim pa la gsum ste /
NK106(me)009:156: lta bas thag bcad pa dang /
NK106(me)009:160: mig yor lta bur rtag tu rnal 'byor /
NK106(me)009:161: yul sems bden med nyin mo rnal 'byor /
NK106(me)009:162: 'dun pas mtshan mo rnal 'byor bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:163: de nas chos thams cad smig rgyu lta bur bstan pa le'u bzhi pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:167: chos thams cad smig rgyu ltar shes par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)009:168: shes nas nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK106(me)009:170: gzhi las 'khrul snang gi shar tshul dang /
NK106(me)009:171: shar dus ji ltar gnas tshul lo //
NK106(me)009:176: gnas lugs 'dzin med chen por bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:177: gnyis pa nyams su blang tshul la gsum ste /
NK106(me)009:180: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi sgom pas grub pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:181: de nas chos thams cad chu zla lta bur bstan pa le'u lnga pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:185: chos thams cad chu zla ltar shes par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)009:186: shes nas nyams su blang ba'o //
NK106(me)009:188: dbyings las sems can gyi 'khrul tshul dang /
NK106(me)009:189: 'khrul dus ji ltar gnas tshul lo //
NK106(me)009:191: dbyings lhun grub chen po las ma rig gzung 'dzin gyi kun rtog g.yos tshul /
NK106(me)009:192: glo bur nyon mongs kyi rang snang 'khrul pa'i 'gro drug 'khor ba'i snang 'grub tshul /
NK106(me)009:193: med snang 'khrul pa'i sems can 'khor ba la rang bzhin shes pa'i snying rje skye tshul lo //
NK106(me)009:195: cir snang gzugs brnyan lta bu /
NK106(me)009:196: yul sems bden med stong pa /
NK106(me)009:197: rig stong chos sku nyag gcig /
NK106(me)009:198: blo bral mnyam pa chen po /
NK106(me)009:201: gzod gnas ye stong phyogs bral /
NK106(me)009:204: skal bzang gzhi lam mthar phyin dus bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:205: gnyis pa shes nas nyams su blang tshul la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)009:210: de nas chos thams cad brag ca lta bur bstan pa'i le'u drug pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:214: chos thams cad brag ca ltar shes par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)009:215: shes nas nyams su blang bar bya ba'o //
NK106(me)009:217: rang bzhin shes pas spyir gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK106(me)009:218: rtogs don nges pas bye brag tu gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK106(me)009:224: gnas lugs brag ca lta bur bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:226: 'dzin med phyogs yan du rtogs pa /
NK106(me)009:227: gtad med yongs grol du rtogs pa /
NK106(me)009:229: rgya chad phyogs bral du rtogs pa'i gdeng tshad nges pa brag ca lta bu'i don bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:230: gnyis pa shes nas nyams su bla nga ba la gsum ste /
NK106(me)009:231: brag stong brag ca ltar blta bas rtag tu rnal 'byor /
NK106(me)009:233: rgyu mtshan bye brag tu dpyad /
NK106(me)009:235: de'i 'bras bu bstan pas nyin mo rnal 'byor /
NK106(me)009:236: rmi lam 'bras bu dang bcas pas mtshan mo rnal 'byor bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:237: de nas chos thams cad dri za'i grong khyer lta bur bstan pa le'u bdun pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:241: chos thams cad dri za'i grong khyer ltar shes par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)009:242: shes nas nyams su blang bar bya ba'o //
NK106(me)009:245: rang bzhin gnas tshul bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:249: 'khrul snang stong dbyings rang snang du bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:251: srid gsum ye stong rnam dag /
NK106(me)009:252: yul sems med pa gsal snang /
NK106(me)009:254: gdod nas rang bzhin skye med /
NK106(me)009:255: nyon mongs kun rtog gzhi bral /
NK106(me)009:259: rnam grol skal bzang mkhas par bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:260: gnyis pa shes nas nyams su blang ba la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)009:261: bden med stong par bsgom pa rtag tu rnal 'byor /
NK106(me)009:262: yul sems rtog med du bsgom pa nyin mo rnal 'byor /
NK106(me)009:263: goms pa'i ngang las shar ba nyams rtogs 'char sgo /
NK106(me)009:264: rtogs pas grol tshad nges pa de'i 'bras bu'o //
NK106(me)009:265: de nas chos thams cad sprul pa ltar bstan pa le'u brgyad pa la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:268: de la gnyis te chos thams cad sprul pa ltar shes par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)009:269: shes nas nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK106(me)009:271: gdod ma'i dbyings las 'khrul tshul dang /
NK106(me)009:272: gzhi med stong pa'i rang bzhin du bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:275: 'khor 'das ye shes kyi rang snang du bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:276: dbyings nyid kun gyi 'char gzhir dbye ba /
NK106(me)009:279: ji bzhin bzhag pas dbyings su gnas pa'o //
NK106(me)009:281: gnas lugs don gyi ngo bo bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:282: mtshan brjod 'das pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:283: rtogs pa nges pa'i gding tshad bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:284: gang las 'byung ba'i khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:290: snang sems gzhi med sprul pa lta bur bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:292: bsam brjod med pa'i rang bzhin spyir bstan pa dang /
NK106(me)009:293: blos brtags chos kyis mi rtog par bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK106(me)009:295: sems snang gzhi med stong pa /
NK106(me)009:297: chos rnams ye grol rtsa bral /
NK106(me)009:300: snang stong sgyu ma rang shar /
NK106(me)009:301: gang snang phyogs yan gtad med /
NK106(me)009:302: dgag sgrub byar med kla nga yangs su bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:304: yid dpyod rtog pa'i dra bar bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:305: de'i dngos su mi rtog par bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:306: rnal don mtshan brjod med par bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:307: blos brtags 'jal byed pho tshod du bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:308: dngos don bla ma'i byin rlabs su bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:309: gsum pa rtogs pa nges pa'i gdeng tshad bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK106(me)009:310: mtha' bral klong yangs rtogs pa'i ngo bor bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:311: 'khor 'das gnyis med rtogs pa'i rang bzhin du bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:312: shar grol 'dzin med rtogs pa'i rang rtsal du bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:313: rang byung ye shes rtogs pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:314: bzhi pa gang las byung ba'i khyad par bstan pa la gsum las /
NK106(me)009:315: byin rlabs yod med kyi rjes su byed pa dang /
NK106(me)009:316: de'i mtshon dpe rtogs pas rtogs pa 'char ba bla
NK106(me)009:317: ma dam pa la rag las par spyir bstan pa
NK106(me)009:319: tha snyad tshig zhen pos sems nyid don gyi snying po bla mas ma zin na /
NK106(me)009:320: dngos su mi rtogs par bye brag tu bshad /
NK106(me)009:321: dam pas zin na rtogs pa gdeng dang bcas pa 'char ba dang /
NK106(me)009:322: brgyud pa byin rlabs dang ldan par brtan par gdams
NK106(me)009:323: pas rgyu mtshan nges pas mkhas grub dam pa bstan
NK106(me)009:325: gnyis pa shes nas nyams su blang ba la gnyis te /
NK106(me)009:327: de las shar ba'i rang bzhin bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:329: g.yo byed gzung 'dzin bral ba'i 'od gsal /
NK106(me)009:330: gsal la rtog pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin re dogs snyems dang bral ba'i gdeng tshad /
NK106(me)009:331: gang yang lam du gyur pa'i rang bzhin /
NK106(me)009:332: mnyam rjes ro gcig 'dres pa'i klong gyur /
NK106(me)009:333: dgongs pa bar mtshams med pa'i gnas lugs /
NK106(me)009:334: rnam bzhi 'khor lo dag pa'i dbang bsgyur /
NK106(me)009:335: rlung sems las su rung ba'i yon tan /
NK106(me)009:336: gnas skabs rtags tshad nges pa'i khyad par /
NK106(me)009:337: nyams rtogs drod tshad nges pa'i 'bras bu /
NK106(me)009:338: skal bzang snod ldan rnams la gdams tshul bstan pa'o //
NK106(me)009:339: spyi don gsum pa bstan bcos yongs su rdzogs pa'i bya ba la gsum ste /
NK106(me)009:340: rlabs chen gzhan don du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)009:341: dben par rang don du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)009:342: gnas gzhan dar rgyas su bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)009:344: dge rtsa bstan bcos kyi rang bzhin /
NK106(me)009:345: sku gsum bde chen du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)009:346: chos sku nyag gcig tu bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)009:348: zhi ba 'phags pa'i dga' tshal du bsngo ba /
NK106(me)009:349: zab mo'i bden mthong ye shes su bsngo ba /
NK106(me)009:350: dal 'byor don yod snying por bsngo ba /
NK106(me)009:351: don gnyis rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)009:353: mdo rgyud snying po'i nges don bstan pa /
NK106(me)009:354: gang gis gang du brtsams tshul brjod pa /
NK106(me)009:355: phyi rabs dad ldan gdul bya la gdams pa /
NK106(me)009:356: chos tshul zab mo dar rgyas su bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)009:357: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso'i bsdus don man+d+aa ra ba'i phreng ba zhes bya ba /
NK106(me)009:360: man ngag gi gnas la snang ba thob cing /
NK106(me)009:361: de kho na nyid kyi don la legs par sbyangs pa'i blo gros rgya che ba /
NK106(me)009:362: theg pa mchog gi rnal 'byor pa dri med 'od
NK106(me)009:363: zer gyis gangs ri thod dkar gyi mgul 'od zer
NK106(me)009:364: sprin gyi skyed mos tshal gyi nang /
NK106(me)009:365: kun tu bzang po'i khang bzangs su chos mthong ba'i
NK106(me)009:366: mig rdul med cing dri ma med pas legs par
NK106(me)009:371: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang chen mdzod //
NK106(me)009:372: bla med mchog gi theg pa 'di //
NK106(me)009:373: ji ltar mkha' la nyi shar bzhin //
